=====Usage notes=====
{{hide box|Usage notes|align=left|
* {{sense|perfective aspect particle}}
: Most of the time, 了 is translated by a [[past tense]]. But it can also indicate that one action is completed before another.
:: {{zh-x|你 吃 了 以後，告訴{su} 我。|Tell me when you are done eating.|in_notes=1}}

* {{sense|change of state particle}}
: When used as the ''change of state particle'', 了 can be translated by [[now]], [[already]] or not [[anymore]].
:: {{zh-x|我 會 說 中文 了。|I can speak Chinese '''now'''. (I couldn't before)|in_notes=1}}
:: {{zh-x|我 吃飯 了。|I've eaten ('''already''').|in_notes=1}}
:: {{zh-x|沒有 紙 了。|There's no paper '''anymore'''.|in_notes=1}}

: In a question, 了 is put before the particle {{zh-l|嗎}}.
}}

